cols_to_remain_KRD=['TRADE_DT','S_INFO_WINDCODE','DURA6M','DURA1Y','DURA2Y','DURA3Y','DURA5Y','DURA7Y','DURA10Y','DURA15Y','DURA20Y']

factor_name=['S','T','B']

##### 
ytm=pd.DataFrame(preprocessing.scale(ytm),index=ytm.index,columns=ytm.columns)

##### PCA
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA
pca=PCA(n_components=3)
ytm_pca=pca.fit_transform(ytm) #  # pca.explained_variance_ratio_   # pca.components_

##### PCA
w=pd.DataFrame(pca.components_,columns=ytm.columns,index=factor_name).drop(columns=cols_to_drop_w)


##### 
KRD=pd.read_csv("BondKeyTermDuration.csv",index_col=0).dropna(axis=1,how='all')[cols_to_remain_KRD]
KRD.TRADE_DT=KRD.TRADE_DT.apply(lambda x:pd.Timestamp(str(x)).date())
KRD.columns=new_cols_name_KRD #  #w.T.plot()

#############  "PCD= w * KRD.T" 
ls=[]
dates=KRD.tradedate.unique()
for i in dates:
    KRD_t=KRD[KRD.tradedate==i].set_index('bondcode').iloc[:,1:]
    df=pd.DataFrame((w.to_numpy()@KRD_t.T.to_numpy()).transpose())
    df['bondcode']=KRD_t.reset_index().bondcode
    df['tradedate']=i
    ls.append(df)
factor=pd.concat(ls,axis=0,ignore_index=True)  # factor)

#factor
factor.columns=factor_name+factor.columns[3:].tolist()
factor=pd.concat([factor[factor.columns[3:].tolist()],factor[factor_name]],axis=1)

fundcodes=pd.read_csv('fund_list.csv').iloc[:,0].map(lambda x:x.split('.')[0])
#
l=[]   # l
for fundcode in fundcodes:
    holdings=finance.run_query(query(finance.FUND_PORTFOLIO_BOND).filter(finance.FUND_PORTFOLIO_BOND.code==fundcode).limit(3000))
    l.append(holdings)  

# 
l=pd.concat(l,axis=0,ignore_index=True).rename(columns={'symbol':'bond','code':'fund'})

# 2020/6/10-- 2020/07/15
dates=f.tradedate.unique()
lst=[]
for date in dates:
    temp=l[l.pub_date<date].groupby(['fund','rank']).last() #date
    temp.insert(loc=0,column='date',value=date)
    lst.append(temp)
holding=pd.concat(lst,axis=0).reset_index()     #6/10-7/15 

#  
holding.proportion=holding.proportion/100
In [550]:
####### 

f['bondcode']=f.bondcode.apply(lambda x:x.split('.')[0]) #f
templist=[]
for date in dates:
    # 
    weights_touse=holding[holding.date==date].pivot_table(index='bond',columns='fund',values='proportion',fill_value=0) 

    #[date, shifttwistbutterfly]
    expo_touse=f[f.tradedate==date].set_index('bondcode')

    #index
    set1=set(weights_touse.index.values)
    set2=set(expo_touse.index.values)
    inter=set1.intersection(set2) #index

    # weightsindexINDEX
    weights=weights_touse.loc[inter][~weights_touse.loc[inter].index.duplicated()].sort_index()
    #  expo_touse()INDEXINDEX
    bond_expo=expo_touse.loc[inter][~expo_touse.loc[inter].index.duplicated()].sort_index()
    #   
    fund_exposure_t=bond_expo.drop(columns=['tradedate']).T@weights
    # 
    fund_exposure_t.insert(0,'tradedate',date)
    #append listb
    templist.append(fund_exposure_t)

#dataframe.
fund_exposure=pd.concat(templist)

# '.OF'
old_columns=fund_exposure.columns.values
new_columns=[i+'.OF' for i in old_columns[1:]]
new_columns.insert(0,old_columns[0])
fund_exposure.columns=new_columns
fund_exposure.tradedate= fund_exposure.tradedate.apply(lambda x:pd.Timestamp(x))

In [551]:
def winsor(x):
    if x.dropna().shape[0] != 0:
        x.loc[x < np.percentile(x.dropna(),5)] = np.percentile(x.dropna(),5)
        x.loc[x > np.percentile(x.dropna(),95)] = np.percentile(x.dropna(),95)
    else:
        x = x.fillna(0)
    return x

##################
ls=[]
for date in fund_exposure.tradedate.unique():
    date=fund_exposure.tradedate.unique()[1]
    expo_t= fund_exposure[fund_exposure.tradedate==date].drop(columns=['tradedate']).T
    expo_t= expo_t.apply(lambda x:winsor(x),axis=0) #
    expo_t= ((expo_t- expo_t.mean())/expo_t.std())  #Z-SCORE
    ls.append(expo_t.T)
df=pd.concat(ls)
df.insert(0,'tradedate',fund_exposure.tradedate)
fund_exposure=df.copy()

##################
# SHIFT 
fund_exposure_shift=fund_exposure.loc['S'].set_index('tradedate').T.unstack()
# TWIST 
fund_exposure_twist=fund_exposure.loc['T'].set_index('tradedate').T.unstack()
# butterfly 
fund_exposure_butterfly=fund_exposure.loc['B'].set_index('tradedate').T.unstack()
